9e479b5e6fa4c11acab","tid":181572,"uid":38798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:51:37.000Z","msg":"dl黎撚下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2030c951ff782918397a8f9905d9382ebc30c6","tid":181572,"uid":38798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:26:13.000Z","msg":"幾好玩，不過有啲難操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇得睇架車咩能力？我見得傳說有寫咩能力，但係其他又冇寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又見架紫車少血過藍車咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，岩岩撞到架傳說船，好撚屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4面開炮仲要我食左一粒炮就爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似特別痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baf14d1dd0606edcab2262fc825f3044817ab02","tid":181572,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾好玩，不過有啲難操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇得睇架車咩能力？我見得傳說有寫咩能力，但係其他又冇寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又見架紫車少血過藍車咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，岩岩撞到架傳說船，好撚屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4面開炮仲要我食左一粒炮就爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似特別痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用緊 4面開炮每面6粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係epic或以上好似冇乜特別能力"},{"pid":"9985c11a88fd4bcbab805e333b1ca3f241e14a8f","tid":181572,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"撞人痛唔痛 速度 轉灣<br />\n架架都唔同但佢冇公開能力值"},{"pid":"3f51d680c57bf110f167c905a8de58076229ac3d","tid":181572,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"我玩左幾日,幾正 <br />\n係火車玩 會好緊張 又驚比人見到<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61c44041cf5fa8fac6fca0a9177d4fd199eadfc","tid":181572,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我玩左幾日,幾正 <br />\n係火車玩 會好緊張 又驚比人見到<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比人見到你玩咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8dd229c0e129643473dbe295275d4f0db35526","tid":181572,"uid":38798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T21:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞人痛唔痛 速度 轉灣<br />\n架架都唔同但佢冇公開能力值</blockquote><br />\n有啲藍車連彎都轉唔到，行到好似小兒麻痺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都中左架紅車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係追縱導彈變3粒果架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ff97311cb99a3651430c0784c01ed76040a622","tid":181572,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撞人痛唔痛 速度 轉灣<br />\n架架都唔同但佢冇公開能力值</blockquote><br />\n有啲藍車連彎都轉唔到，行到好似小兒麻痺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都中左架紅車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係追縱導彈變3粒果架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉急彎可以轉轉下禁埋另一邊<br />\n招skill都幾勁，中晒實死咁濟<br />\n碰碰車都幾好用"},{"pid":"bc94c21f547162b0b92a0eb906aa67f84cd5623e","tid":181572,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20457ed7bfbc24218876b14f041fd7d500f5e88","tid":181572,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我玩左幾日,幾正 <br />\n係火車玩 會好緊張 又驚比人見到<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我會玩到好肉緊<br />\n嚇親人就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 琴日中消防車<br />\n今日中條龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04654d64c4dacee6317de3cb7a4835f82e334a8","tid":181572,"uid":38798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我玩左幾日,幾正 <br />\n係火車玩 會好緊張 又驚比人見到<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我會玩到好肉緊<br />\n嚇親人就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 琴日中消防車<br />\n今日中條龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我中左跑得最快嘅車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得4格血，所以次次拎完噴火器就追住最高分果個黎燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我見親人高分都係用救護車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見親一定燒爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe1ff7370b0fe6c65741419d05cfb2947fbb66b","tid":181572,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"嗰架木乃伊棺材隱藏車大家有冇頭緒"},{"pid":"089e1ecb05a3fbb3217def418df069b033f1a3bb","tid":181572,"uid":56231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"幾好玩，原來抽到重複車，佢會upgrade"}]}